text: Alexander van Hattem (born 6 June 1983) is a Dutch politician who has been a member of the Senate for the Party for Freedom since 2015. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Radboud University Nijmegen alumni Category:Members of the Senate (Netherlands) Category:Party for Freedom politicians Category:21st-century Dutch politicians Category:People from Bergeijk
